CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 3, 1962, pg. C2, reads: "Cited - The above outstanding persons who were presented awards are: left to right: George Hill, Fraternal; Atty. Wilbur C. Douglass, Fraternities; Atty .Joseph W. Givens, Fraternal Service, and J. Edward Trower, Business Establishment."
TitMainTitle: George Hill, Atty. Wilbur C. Douglass, Atty. Joseph W. Givens, and J. Edward Trower, holding award plaques received during Pittsburgh Courier Newspaper's Appreciation Day Rally at Soldiers and Sailors Memorial Hall
